power information of slices in optical spectrum

Total number of slices in Spectrum

Power information of spectrum slice info

OTS-EDM-SPECTRUM-POWER-INFO
first-slice-wavelength: string

Wavelength of first slice

spectrum-slice-spacing: integer

Spacing between spectrum slices

Example
{
  "total-spectrum-slice-count": "integer",
  "spectrum-slice-power-info": [
    {
      "slice-num": "integer",
      "upper-frequency": "integer",
      "lower-frequency": "integer",
      "tx-power": "string",
      "rx-psd": "string",
      "rx-power": "string",
      "tx-psd": "string"
    }
  ],
  "first-slice-wavelength": "string",
  "spectrum-slice-spacing": "integer"
}
